miktex (Source available Implementation of TeX/LaTeX)

MiKTeX is a cross-platform implementation of TeX/LaTeX and
related programs.

Its main features include an integrated package manager that
installs missing components from the Internet, if required.

QT=ON:     Build UI applications (Default is ON).

SYSTEM=ON: Build against system packages (Default is OFF):
development/apache-log4cxx
libraries/libmspack
libraries/uriparser
libraries/zziplib

Post-installation instructions for non-shared (user) setup at
https://miktex.org/howto/install-miktex-unx
